1 county employees shall be shown as lump-sum expenditures by category, including
2 but not limited to road department, jails, solid waste, public safety, and
3 administrative personnel.
4 (4) The financial reporting and publishing requirements for a school district are
5 provided in KRS 160.463.
6 (5) The officer shall procure and include in or attach to the financial statement, as a part
7 thereof, a certificate from the cashier or other proper officer of the banks in which
8 the funds are or have been deposited during the past year, showing the balance, if
9 any, of funds to the credit of the officer making the statement.
10 (6) To provide notice to the public that the city's financial statement has been
11 completed as required by this section, [:
