4 (8) The provisions of this section shall not apply to officers of:
5 (a) A city of the first class;
6 (b) A county containing a city of the first class;
7 (c) A consolidated local government;
8 (d) An urban-county government;
9 (e) A city with a population equal to or greater than twenty thousand (20,000)
